{{Top|leg}}
A '''survival suit''' was an item of armored [[Clothing/Legends|clothing]] designed to protect the wearer against environmental hazards, such as extremes of heat or cold, humidity or dryness, and provided defense against mild radiation. Survival suits were similar in function to [[Environment suit/Legends|enviro-suits]].

A popular model of survival suit was the [[Uni-Environmental Survival Suit]]. [[Vectac Systems, Inc.|Vectac Systems, Incorporated]] produced many types of survival suit during the time of the [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Galactic Empire]].

